Mygine - the NCurses wrapper game engine
======================================================

Mygine provides the following:

	+ State pattern control.
	+ Direct use of ncurses library
	+ Interval based event (1/10 seconds)
	+ A simple example on how mygine is executed

======================================================

Todolist for Mygine:

	+ Actually find a scope for Mygine to focus into
	+ Conduct experiments and tests
	+ Optimize the engine for the specific genre
